Iform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HG\">HG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.1.3</biblScope> </bibl>:—<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅ. τε . . καὶ ἅ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg023:497a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Grg.\">Grg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">497a</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅμ᾽ ἡδέως ἔμοιγε κἀλγεινῶς ἅμα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:436\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.\">Ant.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">436</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n4845.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in Prose <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἅ. δέ . . καί . . , ἅ. τε . . καί . . , ἅ. . . καί</foreign>. . may often be translated by <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">no sooner . . than . . ,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅ. δὲ ταῦτα ἔλεγε καὶ ἀπεδείκνυε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:112\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.112</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ταῦγά τε ἅμα ἠγόρευε καὶ πέμπει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.5</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅ. ἀκηκόαμέν τε καὶ τριηράρχους καθίσταμεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg004.perseus-grc1:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.36</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅ. διαλλάττονται καὶ τῆς ἔχθρας ἐπιλανθάνονται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg011.perseus-grc1:157\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.157</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n4845.3\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἅ. μῦθος ἔην, τετέλεστο δὲ ἔργον</foreign> 'no sooner said than done', <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:242\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.242</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅ. ἔπος τε καὶ ἔργον ἐμήδετο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg004.perseus-grc1:46\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Merc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">46</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ταῦτα εἶπε καὶ ἅ. ἔπος τε καὶ ἔργον ἐποίεε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:134\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.134</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:92\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.92</biblScope> </bibl>: prov., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἅμ᾽ ἔπος ἅμ᾽ ἔργον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0097.tlg001:1:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Diogeni